{"type":"step-attempt","step":"design","sessionId":"18f547c5-9933-48f8-acdd-b4cb0dbd3b23","outcome":{"verdict":"success","findingsPath":null,"error":null,"toolResult":{"ok":true,"reason":"Wrote design.md, spec.md, and tasks.md under specrunner/changes/bite-evidence-forward/ on branch change/bite-evidence-forward-0802ded7.\n\nPlan summary (R4 forward-strategy MVP):\n- OID capture (D1): add StepRun.commitOid captured after finalizeStepArtifacts in runAgentStep; threaded through StepExecutionResult → projectSuccess → pushStepResult AND through StepAttemptRecord/stepRunToRecord/fold — required because the projection strips `steps` from state.json and rebuilds them by folding events.jsonl (resume-safety constraint). Base OID = latest test-materialize run, candidate OID = latest implementer run.\n- BiteEvidence gate (D2): new `bite-evidence` CLI step inserted implementer→bite-evidence→verification in STANDARD_DESCRIPTOR only (fast pipeline untouched). Verdicts passed→verification, strategy-deferred→verification, failed/error→escalate.\n- Isolated execution behind RuntimeStrategy ports (D3): listCommitChangedFiles + runTestsAtCommit (optional on port, required on RealRuntimeStrategy; managed → unavailable), keeping gate decision logic pure/testable.\n- Strategy from request.type only (D4): forward = bug-fix/new-feature; non-forward + non-isolable runtimes defer.\n- Fail-closed (D5): hollow test (base green), candidate red, tamper mismatch, or missing materialized tests → failed → escalate.\n- Tamper (D6): frozen test-cases.md hash from test-case-gen lineage vs current digestArtifacts; mismatch fail-closed, absent→inconclusive (tooth still enforced).\n- Branch-borne BiteEvidence (D7): top-level state.biteEvidence reflected via parseResult→StepCompletion→commitSuccess (pullRequest precedent) + bite-evidence-result.md.\n- Materialized tests only (D8): base-commit changed files minus specrunner/changes & .specrunner.\n\ntasks.md T-01..T-11 covers all 8 request acceptance criteria. Two open questions surfaced (scoped test-command resolution; biteEvidence accumulation vs replacement). No source edits performed — planning only.","status":"success"},"followUpAttempts":0,"transientRetryAttempts":0,"addedTurns":{"reportRetry":0,"postWork":0,"outputRepair":0}},"startedAt":"2026-07-16T12:53:38.550Z","endedAt":"2026-07-16T13:08:23.498Z"}
